jol.types.table
Class HashIndex

java.lang.Object
  jol.types.table.Index
      jol.types.table.HashIndex
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<Index>, java.lang.Iterable<Tuple>
public class HashIndex
extends Index

A hash implementation of an index. The key values are hashed using the Tuple.hashCode() value of the projected tuple. NOTE: Hash collisions are not handled by this structure. A user of this class must apply a further selection, which the query processor already does via the join operation.
